articles.author: Kane Wu
articles.title: Asian stocks slip as China data continues to disappoint - Reuters
articles.description: Asian stocks stumbled on Wednesday, as more disappointing Chinese economic data and the absence of meaningful stimulus from Beijing continued to weigh on investor sentiment.
